body_html:
The latest is an issue that was fixed last week. You will need to sync your code to head and retry.
At this point, this is becoming a technical support issue. It is now clear that this is not a bug in TensorFlow, but rather setup problems in your environment.

Please make sure to follow this page to be able to build TF on windows:
https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_sources_windows
All the solutions to the issues you faced are already documented there.

Closing this issue.
